Sentencas: The intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell (IT-SOFC) is to be realized in shortcoming with the progressing of higher ionic conductivity for electrolyte materials.
Titulo: Comparative effect of REO co-dopant (La, Y, Nd) on ionic conductivity of Gd-doped CeO2 solid electrolyte for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The CeO2-based electrolyte is known to have a high ionic conductivity and is suitable as a solid electrolyte of IT-SOFC with an operation temperature below 700 degrees
Titulo: Comparative effect of REO co-dopant (La, Y, Nd) on ionic conductivity of Gd-doped CeO2 solid electrolyte for IT-SOFC
